-(IBAction)TraslateIng03:(id)sender{
    
    textLegenda03.text = @"Many years ago, an isolated area. A farmer and his family was devoted to corn. He once made ​​his seed across the river in front of his house, within walking distance, but had to go up and down to cross and as the river was very deep was much walking. One day, very tired inadvertently said, 'I would sell my soul to the devil if he were a bridge to the right. - At that time there appeared a well dressed man and said: - You will have the bridge before singing the first cock, and your soul will be mine, but if the cock crows and still not finished, I'll go without your soul. - After closing, the man very distressed and frightened by the fear that would end before she sang the first crow could not sleep, constantly going out to watch the bridge. Surprised by how quickly they were becoming increasingly worried over it, causing the curiosity of his wife asking what was going on. The man told him not to worry her, but such was his desperation he decided platicarle what happened, he surprised by the reaction of his wife who said, 'Lie down and do not worry, leave everything to me, I'll fix you'll see that the devil will take your soul. - the woman got to watch the who built the bridge, when he saw that they were ending, began to pat the legs like a rooster crowed causing all the roosters wake, and began to sing, the devil immediately disappeared. That was how the woman managed to save the soul of her husband and the bridge remained unfinished because the devil disappeared. Many people have wanted to finish it, but have failed because they put party, party falls. They say that only the devil may terminate, but instead of a person's soul.";
    
}
-(IBAction)TraslateIng04:(id)sender{
    
    textLegenda04.text = @"Long ago there was a beautiful maiden, who had married the most handsome young people. All said they were the ideal couple. One morning his friend asked, what good is your wife? 'Excellent beautiful addition to a great cook. What I do not just pleasing is that since we were married I prepared blood sausage. This stranger to friend, who return the next day and said, 'gossip is not gossip, but they told me that's bad. Ask the rocker's why. ' Then the man went and questioned a woman: 'Hey why love always moronga breakfast?' 'Is because my father owns the trail and what is not sold we give it out among the children, my older brother play the visors, my sister feet, blood and me ... for that. ' The man was pleased with that explanation. However, the friend showed up scared, telling the people that everyone knew she was a witch and therefore no one espousing. 'Best friend espíela ... espíela ... and see where he gets the blood sausage. ' She did, and early in the morning before the sun came up, saw his wife got up and walked to the kitchen ... Through the fire saw the figure of his wife. Which in their eyes and unaware of being seen, began to take off the skin and become a ball of fire ... The Young was struck speechless, ran to see his friend and tell what he saw ... 'My friend .... compadre ... out quickly please. 'shouted the young man, who saw his friend without a word took his arm and took him home. There they found the skin of his wife, seeing her friend was left speechless, but in a lucid moment he said: 'quemémosla and may not return and so will no longer be killing more children' And they did. They burned the skin of the girl, who since his return and not find your skin screaming angry and scared at the same time as the morning approached and the sun began to be seen on the horizon. The young man was hidden and very scared when the first rays of the sun burned his wife. ... And this was the end of the nahual of Coyoacan.";
    
}
-(IBAction)TraslateIng05:(id)sender{
    
    textLegenda05.text = @"Many years ago in Tulancingo, Hidalgo., Lived Don Panfilo Garcia, a landowner with great power and immense wealth, 'you say' that had a pact with the Devil. He was owner of 99 properties, after several more attempts, he realized that it was not possible because the want to buy one more, something happened to you, such as cutting, fall, etc., that drove him to buy a ranch, which is in the municipality of Singuilucan, Hidalgo., this new property had tunnels, passages and caves, which only he knew and always took refuge there, to the extent that spent weeks without anyone knowing it, the person who came to fetch him never again see her daughter could not find it, because she had no secrets. They say that Don Panfilo Garcia was mean and cruel to their workers had no right to miss their work, not even sick, because a foul was reason that the threw out the hungry pigs devour they had and the laborers, not listening explanation, and when they asked his staff to give them an extra helping of food, locked in the torture chamber and punishable up to twenty or more days for volviesen will never ask for something. To confess his daughter who was deeply in love with a pawn and his intention of marrying him, in a fit of anger, Don Panfilo so angry that I hit and locked for many months, the peon, ordered him to bring to torture smash, and although his daughter begged him to give him Holy Sepulchre, his father ignored him and he gave the body of love with his daughter in parts before swine to be devoured, his daughter to see such cruelty that his father there are so depressed, that drove him to suicide. Panfilo could not with such great sorrow, because her daughter was as much loved in the world, shortly thereafter, sick, commanded to bring doctors from many places, they know its possible to end, preferring to flee, for if not cured, threw them to the now famous pigs, each passing day more and more sick, it was sad, until he died leaving an enormous fortune, which no person could take a penny because they dared died after to hear the reply of the bells for a long time, the people finally could muster to give you a Holy Sepulchre, at the time of the Church fell out of a tremendous storm, which had to wait for hours to follow the courtship, when they arrived at the cemetery the box began to grind with great force, those attending the funeral, although they were very scared, did not retire until ending up burying it, and there have been tremendous surprise, as when buried, was immediately removed the coffin to the surface after several attempts to bury it, no success yet agreed among all the people, the laborers who were more faithful, to take him to the distant mountains could, carrying all their gold, jewels and money and so many donkeys loaded and Don Panfilo Garcia took him on a cart, after letting in those lares, the laborers would return in donkeys as it was intended to bury him with all his wealth, they say, on their way, the trails were opened and the donkeys began to fall into the void, and the box, you could hear moans and squeaks very strong that you could hear in the distance, to reach the place they had agreed to bury the peons could never leave and return to people going to look for the attack and decided to stay with his master as 'Hermit', then killed them, were embodied in stone and, looking horror of what are surely lived over time, the area is east of Tulancingo, a side of the hill The Yolo. They say that part of his fortune is buried in the garden of the estate Exquitlán, guarded by elves still dwell in it, who may come when the moon is full and twelve o'clock this cave exactly where the shadow of the cross of the chapel before being devoured by the goblins will own the fortunes of Don Panfilo Garcia. The Saints of the chapel are offered up to the Devil, because they worshiped, to the Angels instead of harp have a pitchfork and the Virgin is with hands on chest adoring gaze downward.";
    
}
-(IBAction)TraslateIng06:(id)sender{
    
    textLegenda06.text = @"In the Old Town, according to the chronicles and the voices inherited from generation to generation, always lived in perfect harmony. The families were residents in the urban space were as one, both joyous events such as those marked by pain. Religiosity characterized the people of those days was required daily Mass attendance of five or taking place throughout the day at Cathedral, certainly, could not miss the rosary or holy time for many years Jardón father-founder of the Marian Congregation, held exclusively for men. Jardón Andrew, his brother, recited the rosary at wakes the neighbors and accompanied them to the cemetery to pray it to the grave. Also attended church or other pious acts, the chapel of the College of San Jose, neighbors in the wing that gave Abasolo and domestic students on the ship that looked onto the courtyard. For many decades lived in the Old Town, other than parent Jardon, whom people saw pass surrounded by children and by floating its huge black-layer, Canon John Trevino, better known as 'the father Juanito', and Father John Jose Hinojosa, whom not a few were levitated not only celebrating the offices, but also when walking down the street with his ascetic countenance. During the summer rigor sidewalks populated rocking chairs and Austrian or Malinche. There was greeted warmly Don Celedonio Junco, which passed with the newspaper under his arm, or General Garza Ayala, who, to tell the doctor Gonzalitos, handled the pen as well as the sword. Meanwhile, the boys were playing in the street safely to tag, hide and seek, the happy or the donkey jumped. Birthdays and holy days of young and old were of living and joy in the snack and the naive piñata; like flooding was observed during the holidays in the inns and pastorals. Each house had a piano or playing an instrument like the violin and guitar. They were famous gatherings of the house of Don Celedonio Junco, songs, poems and improvisations were the delight of the audience. Meanwhile, the girls were estudiantinas and participating in civic and social parties. Such was the joy and strangers to the area called 'the Triana district.' It was common in addition to the commentary on political events or the Revolution, or the last chapter of the serial novel that included The Guardian, embroider conversation about what happened in the neighborhood: the girl who fell from the balcony, Don Genaro he left his shop and never returned, the young man who was his horse bolted and dragged him several feet, and so on. Some events were violent tinge, like the officer who demanded to vacate Castillon family home in 24 hours, to stay in it Carranza, without knowledge of it. Others were comical in nature, like the girl made with her boyfriend agreed to take flight and to identify a green mantle. His grandmother, the only person I would go to mass at five, and that would be the appropriate time to escape. But the grandmother took the mantle of the granddaughter, who pretended to sleep. The sweetheart, to identify the mantle, took her in his arms and mounted his horse, but the lantern-first realized the confusion. They say that the grandmother was ecstatic rider's arms. Legend also has dominion in the neighborhood. Noises, footsteps and shadows are heard and seen in old houses. Bones buried in the trunk of the walnut secret tunnels to the cathedral to school, women sandwiched in the thick walls, crowns images to rub wishes come true, pianos playing themselves, or some gentleman in debt than almost suicidal in the north gate of the cathedral to a bishop who gives the sum of money to save the compromise. History, tradition and legend, that was the Old Town through the centuries. Its significance and rescue refunded to Monterrey this beautiful wisp of her past.";
    
}
-(IBAction)TraslateIng07:(id)sender{
    
    textLegenda07.text = @"They say the two gay buddies were walking as usual after leaving the bar at 2 or 3 am, and went reeling spring as much as your body gets the permit. The fact is that when they would come to the neighborhood where they lived, they saw in the distance a woman dressed in white or girlfriend, the joke is that by seeing the friend of my grandfather, who was a bachelor, he told my grandfather 'Now if I found my friend and godmother', for which my grandfather replied, 'do not invent my friend!As a woman as she is set on a man like you! Let's go now to my friend's house '. In total fool, the friend decided to go after that woman, so my grandfather could not leave it alone and was followed, at the end of walk 5 or 6 streets, a neighbor who was a factory watchman saw them at 2 gentlemen singing and shouting, along of course with this beautiful woman. According to my grandfather's mouth was so, to which Mr. they cry that they were going and they ignored him, so he's been following. Because as everyone knows at that time were few who cared for each other is totally the pedestal they cry so hard to heed it, that my grandfather and his friend turned to him, but when he returned his gaze to the woman were right on the edge of a ravine, which by his drunken logic are under fear. From that day and so far have been around 30 or 50 men who died in the ravine, nobody knows anything about this lady and who is and where it comes, the only thing I can say is that in the ravine something terrible happened.";
    
}
-(IBAction)TraslateIng08:(id)sender{
    
    textLegenda08.text = @"In Naranjillos was a very pretty girl who had just left an orphan. One day her friend came to tell who had seen his mother in the Neighborhood Road, near the village. She did not believe what your friend said, 'is quite dead and buried,' he replied. However, her friend was not alone in seeing the apparition, many ladies of the town were found in the way of the Neighborhood to the lady dressed in black, dirty, muddy and matted hair. They asked him who he was or who was looking for, but the black woman did not answer, everyone thought it was dumb. Women still seen wandering up and down in the way of Neighborhood and people began to realize that it was a lost soul. The friend of the girl was talking to her: 'Is your mom, I know' said the friend. 'But if she's dead'-claimed the girl. 'Is it safe walking grieving ... Have you taken good care of your brothers? ' He asked with some timidity. The girl did not like the question, and it was getting nervous. The next day a lady of the people he met the girl who brought face unveiled, and in general, a deplorable aspect. 'See if you are leaving this man married!' Suddenly snapped the lady. 'Go look after your brothers and let rest the soul of your mother who walks in grief.' She shivered, as indeed was the mistress of a man married and went with him all night, so that in the morning was not able to care for their siblings or go to work. Heartbroken, decided to go the way of the Neighborhood to see if it was true what they said. Upon arrival, found the woman in black, came and acknowledged it was his mother. The woman began to mourn, he said nothing, but she felt that her mother knew everything, had always been so, guess their emotions and thoughts. The black woman soothed her crying and was lost at the bottom of the road. She felt the void left by her mother and warned that his appeal had been crying. In order to get rid of guilt, went to find her lover and said he would never see him again, then went